      "name": "施法Spellcasting",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The orc is a 5th-level 施法者spellcaster.<br>Its 施法施法属性spellcasting ability is Wisdom (法术豁免DCspell save DC<br>13, +5 to hit with 法术攻击spell attack). The orc has the<br>following cleric spells prepared:<br>戏法Cantrips (随意at will): 抵抗resistance, 神圣烈焰sacred flame, 神奇术thaumaturgy<br>1st level (4 法术位slots): 治愈伤口cure wounds, 引导之矢guiding bolt, 施加创伤inflict wounds<br>2nd level (3 法术位slots): 致盲/致聋blindness/deafness, 灵能武器（大斧）spiritual weapon (greataxe)<br>3rd level (2 法术位slots): 赋予诅咒bestow curse, 守护灵spirit guardians</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
